<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
  <!-- Template Header -->
  <%= erb :header %>

  <!-- Page Stylesheets/Scripts -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/jobs.css">
</head>

<body>
  <!-- Template Navbar -->
  <%= erb :navbar %>

  <div class="wrapper">
    <div id="contactStrip">
      <h1>CONTACT US</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="info">

      <h2>Join our team!</h2>

      <p>Working with Show Star Entertainments is one of the 
      best ways to make some extra money and be part of a huge 
      social team whilst meeting loads of new people!</p>

      <p>As one of Loughborough's longest running, diverse and 
      consistent events companies, Show Star Entertainments offers many 
      different branded events held across all the best venues in town 
      and are responsible for nights such as XO Thursdays, 
      Mayhem, Bad Manners and Selected Sounds.</p>

      <p>Our ever growing brand XO Thursdays is also launching in Leeds and Nottingham this year!</p>

      <p>We have loads of different part time roles for you to get involved in such as:-</p>

      <ul>
        <li>Promotions & Events Managers</li>
        <li>Ticket Reps/Gueslist Reps/brand reps (networkers)</li>
        <li>Event Staff (till staff, VIP hosts, cloakroom staff)</li>
        <li>Flyering Staff</li>
        <li>Djâ€™s</li>
        <li>Photographers</li>
        <li>Videographers</li>
        <li> Graphic Designer's</li>
        <li>Or anyone with any sort of talent that may want to get involved </li>
      </ul>

      <p>For all enquiries please fill out the contact form below and we will be in touch soon</p>

    </div>

    <div class="jobs-wrapper">
      <form class="jobs-form" action="mailto:showstarents@live.co.uk" method="post" enctype="text/plain">
        Name:<br/>
        <input type="text" placeholder="Full Name" name="name"><br/>
        City:<br/>
        <select type="select" name="city">
          <option>Loughborough</option>
          <option>Leeds</option>
          <option>Nottingham</option>
        </select><br/>
        Date of Birth:<br/>
        <input type="date" name="dateofbirth" /><br/>
        Mobile Number:<br/>
        <input type="text" placeholder="Mobile Number" name="number"><br/>
        Email Address:<br/>
        <input type="email" placeholder="Email" name="email"><br/>
        Facebook Url:<br/>
        <input type="text" placeholder="http://" name="facebook"><br/>
        Roles you're interested in:<br/>
        <textarea class="enquiry" type="textarea" placeholder="DJ, Event Staff, etc.." name="roles"></textarea><br>
        Other Information/About you:<br/>
        <textarea class="enquiry" type="textarea" placeholder="A bit about you" name="otherinfo"></textarea><br>
        <input id="sendEmail" type="submit" value="Send with Mail Client">
      </form>
    </div>

    <div id="socialLinksDiv">
      <a href="https://twitter.com/showstarents">
        <img id="twitterLink" class="socialLink" src="images/twitterlogo.png">
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.facebook.com/ShowStarEntertainments/?fref=photo">
        <img id="facebookLink" class="socialLink" src="images/facebooklogo.png">
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/showstarents/">
        <img id="instagramLink" class="socialLink" src="images/instagramlogo.png">
      </a>
    </div>



  </div> 

</body>
</html>
